1. **Removed all `#pragma HLS ARRAY_PARTITION complete`** from workload: The complete partitioning of `l_fx`, `l_fy`, `l_fz`, `l_px`, `l_py`, `l_pz` was creating 256 independent register arrays per force/position component (2.3x FF overhead). Removing these partitions keeps arrays in block RAM (contributing to the 122 BRAM in gold baseline), dramatically reducing FF and LUT usage.

