3. **Reduced inner loop unroll from full (factor=16) to factor=2**: Changed `#pragma HLS UNROLL` to `#pragma HLS UNROLL factor=2`. This reduces DSP usage by ~75% (from 2368 to ~600), as the loop body with expensive division and multiplication operations is no longer fully unrolled.

